      <textblock>
        Dentine hypersensitivity (DH) is characterized by a short, sharp pain arising from exposed
        dentin.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age and between 18 - 60

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Caries

          -  Defective restorations

          -  Full crowns

